{"article_id":"huSqcDT8MmjllPKr","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump and CBS News White House correspondent Weijia Jiang , an Asian American reporter , had a heated exchange on Monday at a press conference .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Jiang asked","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"why the Trump administration was boasting about its coronavirus-testing numbers","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"and comparing the US with other countries .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"`` Why does that matter ?","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Why is this a global competition to you","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"if every day Americans are still losing their lives","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"and we 're still seeing more cases every day , ''","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Jiang asked Trump .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"`` Well , they 're losing their lives everywhere in the world .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"And maybe that 's a question","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"you should ask China , ''","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"`` Do n't ask me .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Ask China that question .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"OK ?","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"When you ask them that question ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"you may get a very unusual answer . ''","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"President Donald Trump and a CBS News White House correspondent had a tense exchange on Monday during a White House press conference at the Rose Garden .","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"Trump on Monday spoke in front of a large sign","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that said","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"`` AMERICA LEADS THE WORLD IN TESTING ''","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"and gave a glowing assessment of the country 's efforts","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"to test its citizens for the coronavirus .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"`` If people want to get tested ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"they get tested , ''","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"The Trump administration regularly says","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"the US leads other countries in the number of coronavirus tests","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"administered .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"While the number surpasses that of tests in other countries ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"it severely lags others in terms of tests","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"completed per capita .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"As of late April , Italy administered nearly 21,000 tests per million people ,","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"compared with the US 's 11,800 .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"CBS 's Weijia Jiang , an Asian American reporter , asked Trump","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"why his administration was touting its coronavirus-testing numbers","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"and comparing them with other countries ' totals .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"`` Why does that matter ?","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Why is this a global competition to you","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"if every day Americans are still losing their lives","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"and we 're still seeing more cases every day , ''","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Jiang asked Trump .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"who has previously had heated exchanges with Jiang during press conferences ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"told her to ask China .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"The Communist Party of China has been accused of distorting the number of coronavirus-related cases and deaths in the country and downplaying concerns during the outbreak 's early stages in December ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"before it became a pandemic .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"`` Well , they 're losing their lives everywhere in the world .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"And maybe that 's a question","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"you should ask China , ''","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"`` Do n't ask me .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Ask China that question .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"OK ?","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"When you ask them that question ,","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"you may get a very unusual answer . ''","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Trump attempted to take a question from another reporter ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"but Jiang hit back :","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"`` Sir , why are you saying that to me , specifically -","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that I should ask China ? ''","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Jiang was born in China","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"and raised in the US","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"after her parents immigrated to the country","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"when she was 2 years old .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"`` I 'm not saying it specifically to anybody , ''","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"`` I 'm saying it to anybody","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"that would ask a nasty question like that . ''","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"`` That 's not a nasty question , ''","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Jiang said .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"`` Why does it matter ? ''","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Trump ignored the comment","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"and appeared to call on CNN White House correspondent Kaitlan Collins ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"who was seated near Jiang .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"`` I just want to let my colleague finish ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"but can I ask you a question ? ''","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"Collins said ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"appearing to refer to Jiang .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"Trump then skipped over Collins","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"and asked for other questions .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Trump abruptly ended the press conference soon afterward .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"All the press members were wearing face masks","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"after the White House issued new guidance on safety measures .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Trump previously berated Jiang and her network during a separate press conference in April .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"During the exchange , Trump expressed frustration at China 's coronavirus response","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"and said :","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"`` It should have been told to us early . ''","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Jiang focused in on the administration 's response to the pandemic ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"when Trump issued travel restrictions ,","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"`` the virus was already here '' in the US .","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"`` How many cases were in the United States","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"when I did my ban ? ''","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"Trump asked .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"As Jiang attempted to respond ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"Trump told her to keep her `` voice down , please . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":115,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":0,"right":114,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":114,"left":100,"right":113,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":1,"right":99,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":104,"right":112,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":103,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":4,"right":102,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":5,"right":101,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":9,"right":111,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":106,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":105,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclea